  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0dad \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dca \u0da0\u0dc3\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dca 100 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db6\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A Railway Reserve Perchase is leased at Rs 100 per annum",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Transport Minister Bandula Gunawardena said today (03) in Polonnaruwa that permission will be given for short-term crop cultivation in railway reserves.",
        "The minister said that it will be given under the tax concession system and thus one hundred rupees will be charged for a perch per year.",
        "The minister said this while attending a mobile service program held at Polonnaruwa Pulatisi Chandra Mandapa regarding the existing problems related to railway reserves in Tamankaduwa Divisional Secretariat of Polonnaruwa District.",
        "\"Mr. President and Prime Minister, we all the cabinet took a decision. Due to the urgent need for cultivation due to this food crisis, we will give to farmer organizations under railway reserve lease basis for short-term crop cultivation, where we charge one hundred rupees per perch per year and if ten perches are leased, Rs. Burns.",
        "You can grow it for a year for a thousand rupees, but you can't build a plant like that to keep honey plants. You can't do any construction, only plant chillies. Potatoes, sweet potatoes, other crops that grow in the dry zone. Go and meet the regional secretary and talk to him and implement this.\"",
        "Meanwhile, the Minister of Transport added that it is hoped to add several tourist train journeys from Colombo to several areas in order to develop the tourism industry.",
        "The minister also gave tax licenses to the people currently residing in the railway reserves."
      ],
